      "releaseNotes": "We’ve been busy soaking up the summer sun and optimizing our tech! We’ve given the app a performance refresh—think of it as a cool breeze for your shopping experience. Faster loading, smoother navigation, and an even quicker checkout await. Grab the update and dive into the season’s best deals!",
